news.author: Joe Parkinson, Drew Hinshaw
news.title: How #BringBackOurGirls Became an International Rallying Cry
news.description: In 2014, more than 200 Nigerian schoolgirls were kidnapped. It hardly made global headlines—until a Twitter hashtag took off.

news.author: Jon Porter
news.title: Amazon’s cashierless tech expands to London with first international store
news.description: Amazon has opened its first cashier-less store outside of the US with a new Amazon Fresh location in London. The store uses the company’s Just Walk Out technology. Billing is handled automatically.
